msgstr ""
"在没有配置其他图形界面时，FreeBSD 开机时将自动进入命令行登入界面，就像下面这"
"样："

#. type: delimited block . 4
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:81
#, no-wrap
