#. type: Plain text
#: documentation/content/en/books/handbook/basics/_index.adoc:302
#, fuzzy
#| msgid ""
#| "The shell provides the user's default environment for interacting with "
#| "the system. There are many different kinds of shells and experienced "
#| "users will have their own preferences, which can be reflected in their "
#| "account settings."
msgid ""
"The shell provides the user's default environment for interacting with the "
